&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/10/titian-rape-of-europa.webp" alt="">&lt;em>The Rape of Europa (c. 1560-62), Titian&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Europe is in great danger, it faces a moment of profound vulnerability (&lt;strong>Titian &amp;rsquo;s &amp;lsquo;Rape of Europa&amp;rsquo;&lt;/strong> seemed apt).&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>The Overlapping Crises of Climate Change, Biodiversity Loss and Political Dishonesty</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/20/the-overlapping-crises-of-climate-change-biodiversity-loss-and-political-dishonesty/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Oct 2025 12:06:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/20/the-overlapping-crises-of-climate-change-biodiversity-loss-and-political-dishonesty/</guid><description>&lt;p>This article has been created using a new public AI Notebook:&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/54e6fcc6-7310-4ad5-a9de-ae70b972c6af">Climate Change, Ecological Disaster and Civilisational Risks&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The Notebook features a range of key scientific and cultural sources. The complexity of these issues and depth of the data lends itself to a publicly available database for people to conduct their own queries. I hope it is useful, particularly for a new generation more interested in solving the problems we face than getting rich whilst watching the world burn.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Green Energy: Delay for Another Day</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/16/green-energy-delay-for-another-day/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Oct 2025 11:30:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/16/green-energy-delay-for-another-day/</guid><description>&lt;p>This AI assisted blog synthesises some of the information contained within a public &lt;a href="https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/e25aca97-46e0-4171-b36a-ff0355424cd3">&lt;strong>Google Notebook&lt;/strong>&lt;/a> I created to triage submissions made to the &lt;a href="https://www.aph.gov.au/Parliamentary_Business/Committees/Senate/Information_Integrity_on_Climate_Change_and_Energy/ClimateIntegrity">Australian Select Committee on Information Integrity on Climate Change and Energy&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I was inspired by a comment of &lt;a href="https://bsky.app/profile/jksteinberger.bsky.social">Dr Julia Steinberger&lt;/a> (though she did not suggest using AI). I created the AI Notebook to help people (including students, journalists, scientists, policymakers) easily access and query the 227 submissions made to the Select Committee to help review how industry bodies and experts respond to the climate crisis and energy debate.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Project 2025 &amp; the Urgent Need for A Defence of American Democracy</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/15/project-2025-the-need-for-an-urgent-defence-of-american-democracy/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Oct 2025 13:16:01 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/10/15/project-2025-the-need-for-an-urgent-defence-of-american-democracy/</guid><description>&lt;p>Progress Update&lt;/p>
